import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card';
import CardGroup from 'react-bootstrap/CardGroup';
import KeeperFoto from "../images/KeeperAppTest.png"

function ProjectCards() {
  return (
    <CardGroup className='Card'>
      <Card>
        <Card.Img style={{height:"250px"}} variant="top" src={KeeperFoto}/>
        <Card.Body>
          <Card.Title>Website</Card.Title>
          <Card.Text>
           React, CSS, Bootstrap, HTML
          </Card.Text>
          <Card.Text>
          This Website
          </Card.Text>
        </Card.Body>
      </Card>
      <Card>
        <Card.Img variant="top" src="holder.js/100px160" />
        <Card.Body>
          <Card.Title>Keeper App</Card.Title>
          <Card.Text>
          React, CSS, HTML
          </Card.Text>
          <Card.Text>
          I dont know what is is tbh
          </Card.Text>
        </Card.Body>
      </Card>
      <Card>
        <Card.Img variant="top" src="holder.js/100px160" />
        <Card.Body>
          <Card.Title>ToDo List</Card.Title>
          <Card.Text>
          HTML, CSS, NodeJS, Express
          </Card.Text>
          <Card.Text>
          A nice little todo list for everyday use
          </Card.Text>
        </Card.Body>
      </Card>
    </CardGroup>
  );
}

export default ProjectCards;
